benefits.benefit_highlight_body: Check out the benefits other Starbucks Odyssey members have received.
benefits.benefit_info:
Earn Points to unlock Benefit Levels all year long.
The higher your Level, the better the Benefits.
benefits.benefit_info_new: By completing Journeys and collecting Stamps, Starbucks Odyssey members earn points and unlock benefit levels. When you've unlocked a level, choose one benefit during a Benefit Selection Period. Your points balance and level will not decrease after making a selection.
benefits.benefit_recap_body: The second Benefit Selection Period is a wrap. See some of the incredible milestones the community hit.
benefits.benefit_tree_name_body: Check out some of the names members chose for the trees at our Hacienda Alsacia farm.
benefits.benefits_begin: This selection period ended on December 10th, 2023. Keep an eye out for exciting new benefits coming in 2024!

feedingAmerica.body: Help provide 50 meals to neighbors facing hunger.

confirmation.body: Thank you so much for your generosity. We will be donating to Feeding America to help end hunger and you’ll soon receive an update on the collective impact.

feedingAmerica.headline: Feeding America Donation

1.body: We will make a donation to Feeding America on your behalf, helping to provide 50 meals* to neighbors facing hunger.
1.headline: Feeding America Donation

2.body: By clicking below, you are confirming your selection of a donation to Feeding America<sup>®</sup>*. Confirming is final and cannot be undone.

freeCoffeeForAMonth.headline: 30 Days of Free Drinks

1.body: Free Starbucks drinks, anyone? Every day for 30 days, you'll receive a coupon in your Starbucks app that can be redeemed for one free beverage up to $10.
1.disclaimer:
Items redeemed per this Benefit do not count toward completion of a Starbucks Odyssey Journey activity.

Between 5/11 and 6/9, members who select this benefit can enjoy a free Starbucks beverage ($10 limit) once a day at a participating store by using the coupon in their Starbucks Rewards account. These coupons are valid for all handcrafted beverages, excluding alcohol and canned or bottled beverages. A coupon not used on any given day does not carry over to the next day.
1.headline:
30 Days of
Free Drinks

2.body: By clicking below, you are confirming your selection of 30 Days of Free Drinks. Confirming is final and cannot be undone.

Unlock an experience for you and a guest at a Starbucks Reserve store of your choice - New York, Chicago, or Seattle.

1.body: A new Benefit Selection Period begins August 21st-27th. Get a first look at the benefits available to Starbucks<sup>®</sup> Odyssey members.
1.headline: Sneak Peek of Benefits

2.body:
What exactly are benefits? They're exclusive experiences, merch, product or philanthropic opportunities you can only access as a Starbucks® Odyssey member. Think free coffee, unique events at Starbucks Reserve® Roasteries, virtual coffee classes, and so much more.

Unlock benefits levels by earning points as you complete Journeys or collecting Stamps. The more points you have, the more benefit options you can select from. You can select one benefit per selection period.
2.headline: Benefits 101
